---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="smart-start-hero">
    <div class="smart-start-hero-content">
      <div class="smart-start-image-wrapper">
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Website%20Smart%20start%20header-o3O0F42PMslRXtuA00yX6sTZGZdpeL.jpg" alt="Multi-generational family" class="family-image" />
      </div>
      <div class="smart-start-branding">
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Logo_Smart%20Start%20-%20White%402x-XsgqCSJBhoO4brk80RcacqCWNvp7mx.png" alt="Smart Start" class="smart-start-logo" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="smart-start-description">
    <div class="description-container">
      <p class="description-text">
        Smart Start is TechNest's community program created to give back to the Chicagoland area we are proud to call home. Each month we choose one household or small business to receive a complimentary smart technology upgrade that makes everyday life a little easier, safer or more enjoyable. The program is built on genuine care, local impact and the belief that everyone deserves comfort, security and convenience. Anyone can enter or nominate a neighbor, and every Smart Start project highlights how thoughtful, well installed technology can create real change for real people in our community.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="how-it-works">
    <div class="how-it-works-container">
      <h2 class="how-it-works-title">HOW IT WORKS</h2>
      
      <div class="how-it-works-intro">
        <p>Smart Start is designed to be simple for everyone in the Chicagoland community. Each month, we select one household or small business to receive a complimentary smart technology upgrade that makes a real difference in their everyday life. Anyone can enter or nominate someone else, and the process is straightforward from start to finish.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="steps-container">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Enter or nominate</h3>
          <p class="step-description">Complete a short form about yourself or someone you would like to nominate and explain how a smart upgrade would make everyday life easier.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Review and selection</h3>
          <p class="step-description">Every entry is carefully reviewed. Each month we select one household or small business where technology can genuinely improve comfort, safety or convenience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Plan the solution</h3>
          <p class="step-description">We speak with the selected recipient, assess their space and design the right smart solution. We take care of the products and planning.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Install and support</h3>
          <p class="step-description">Our team installs everything with care and makes sure it works properly, leaving the recipient confident and comfortable using it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">5</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Share the impact</h3>
          <p class="step-description">With your permission, we share the story to show how thoughtful technology can make a real difference.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .smart-start-hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0072cc 0%, #0052a3 100%);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    margin: 0;
    width: 100vw;
    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
    margin-top: 70px;
  }

  .smart-start-hero-content {
    max-width: 1400px;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .smart-start-image-wrapper {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .family-image {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 450px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .smart-start-branding {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .smart-start-logo {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .smart-start-description {
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    background-image: url('/background-shapes.png');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-attachment: fixed;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .description-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .description-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #0072cc;
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Anek Latin', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .how-it-works {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0072cc 0%, #0052a3 100%);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    width: 100vw;
    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
  }

  .how-it-works-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .how-it-works-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #fafafa;
    text-align: left;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    font-family: 'Anek Latin', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .how-it-works-intro {
    color: #fafafa;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-family: 'Anek Latin', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .how-it-works-intro p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .steps-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .step-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .step-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    color: #fafafa;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-family: 'Anek Latin', sans-serif;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #fafafa;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    font-family: 'Anek Latin', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .step-description {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #fafafa;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-family: 'Anek Latin', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .smart-start-hero-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .smart-start-image-wrapper {
      flex: 1;
      max-width: 350px;
    }

    .family-image {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .smart-start-branding {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .smart-start-logo {
      max-width: 500px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .smart-start-hero {
      min-height: auto;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      margin-top: 70px;
    }

    .smart-start-hero-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .smart-start-image-wrapper {
      max-width: 300px;
    }

    .family-image {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .smart-start-branding {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .smart-start-logo {
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    .smart-start-description {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .description-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .how-it-works {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }

    .how-it-works-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .how-it-works-intro {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .steps-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
